<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Email Verification OTP</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding-bottom: 30px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #D4AF37;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #D4AF37;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        .otp-box {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .otp-code {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            background-color: #FFF8E7;
            border: 2px dashed #D4AF37;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .info-box {
            background-color: #F0F9FF;
            border: 1px solid #BAE6FD;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #0C4A6E;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding-top: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 12px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f4f4f4;">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header">
                <h1>🎨 Artist Email Verification</h1>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <p>Hi {{username}},</p>
                <p>
                    Thank you for applying to become an artist on <strong>ArtVPP</strong>!
                    To verify your email address, please use the OTP below.
                </p>

                <div class="otp-box">
                    <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
                </div>

                <p style="text-align: center; color: #666;">
                    This OTP is valid for <strong>{{validMinutes}} minutes</strong>.
                </p>

                <div class="info-box">
                    <strong>ℹ️ Note:</strong> This OTP is to verify your email as part of your artist application.
                    Once verified, your application will be reviewed by our team.
                    If you did not apply to become an artist, please ignore this email.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© {{year}} ArtVPP. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>This is an automated message, please do not reply.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

